Care management for those away from home

#proxy isn't set up to receive care in #region.


Select Add region if youd like this person to receive care in this region and then you can manage this persons care.


If not, select Not now if youd like to continue managing only your care in #region.

If you've already requested this region of care, youll receive an email within 20 minutes notifying you of when weve successfully added it. Tap or select Close to exit this window.

Sorry, you currently cant add Washington as a region of care for #proxy. Either youre not set up to manage care for #proxy or #proxy isnt set up to receive care in Washington.


You can still manage your own care in Washington.

 

Select continue to go on managing your care. Or select cancel to close this window.

 

Washington residents outside Vancouver/Longview requiring further assistance can contact Member Services at 1-888-874-1620 or 711 (TTY), available Monday through Friday, 8 a.m. to 5 p.m., except major holidays.
